.el .ds Aq '
.TH agentguard 1  "agentguard " 
.SH NAME
agentguard \- AgentGuard Security Scanner & MCP Server
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBagentguard\fR [\fB\-\-logs\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIsubcommands\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
AgentGuard Security Scanner & MCP Server
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-logs\fR
Enable quality logging for scan results and critic decisions
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
agentguard\-mcp(1)
Runs the AgentGuard MCP Server
.TP
agentguard\-scan(1)
Scans a directory for vulnerabilities
.TP
agentguard\-auth(1)
Manage LLM authentication credentials in the OS keychain
.TP
agentguard\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
